headline: PPL Earnings Miss Estimates in Q4, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: PPL's Q4 EPS misses estimates but revenues rise 2.8% y/y. It boosts the infrastructure plan to $23 billion and guides 2026 earnings of $1.90-$1.98.

headline: IDACORP Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: IDA posts Q4 earnings beat as customer growth lifts profit. It unveils the 2026 EPS outlook of $6.25-$6.45 and plans up to $1.5B in capex.
